    "The top-k relevant passages are returned, enabling dynamic, on-demand knowledge augmentation at each step.",
    "Extractor Agent.",
    "Retrieved passages often contain redundant or irrelevant content.",
    "Instead of appending entire chunks, the Extractor selects and aggregates sentences or spans directly aligned with the current subquery.",
    "This not only filters out noise and mitigates the lost-in-the-middle issue (Liu et al., 2024a), but also enables effective evidence aggregation by combining complementary information from multiple sources into a concise evidence set for the QA agent."
